text:
Tired, Yuika?
Once we finish shooting, feel free to change.

Oh! Yeah, okay.
...Hey, did you think it's unusual to take selfies now?

Huh? Um, not really...
It's not that unusual.

Huh, seems like there's something implied there.
Well... I've been doing a bit of research.

...From now on, I'm sure there will be plenty of
opportunities for people to see this outfit, so...

I thought you might like
to know what it looks like.

Ah, I see. ...Well, if that's the case,
take your time with your research.

Thank you for your consideration!
But we've pretty much finished shooting.

...Oh! Since we're here,
maybe I should have P-tan check the photos too?
